


# migadu

IMAPAccount migadu
Host imap.migadu.com
Port 993
User server@benlab.ca
PassCmd "pass show migadu.com_events | head -1"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore migadu-remote
Account migadu

MailDirStore migadu-local
Path ~/Mail/server@benlab.ca/
Inbox ~/Mail/server@benlab.ca/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/server@benlab.ca/Trash
SubFolders Verbatim

channel migadu
Master :migadu-remote:
Slave :migadu-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
Remove Both
CopyArrivalDate yes

# mailbox.org

IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
Port 993
User benoit@benoitj.ca
PassCmd "pass show mailbox.org | head -1"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Account mailbox

MailDirStore mailbox-local
Path ~/Mail/mailbox.org/
Inbox /home/benoit/Mail/mailbox.org/Inbox
Trash /home/benoit/Mail/mailbox.org/Trash
SubFolders Verbatim

channel mailbox
Master :mailbox-remote:
Slave :mailbox-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
Remove Both
CopyArrivalDate yes

